import React, { Component } from 'react';
import TextField from '@material-ui/core/TextField';
import { withStyles } from '@material-ui/core/styles';
import Dialog from '@material-ui/core/Dialog';
import DialogActions from '@material-ui/core/DialogActions';
import DialogContent from '@material-ui/core/DialogContent';
import DialogContentText from '@material-ui/core/DialogContentText';
import DialogTitle from '@material-ui/core/DialogTitle';
import { Button } from '@material-ui/core';

const styles = theme => ({
    marginRight: 15
});    

class AddPessoa extends Component { 
    
    state = {
        open: false    
    }

    render() {

        return(
            <Dialog
            open={this.props.open}
            >
                <DialogTitle>Adicionar</DialogTitle>
                <DialogContent>
                <DialogContentText>
                    Preencha os campos abaixo para adicionar uma nova pessoa
                </DialogContentText>
                    <TextField
                        autoFocus
                        margin="dense"
                        id="nome"
                        label="Nome"
                        type="text"
                        fullWidth
                    />
                    <TextField
                        margin="dense"
                        id="cpf"
                        label="CPF"
                        type="text"
                        fullWidth
                    />
                    <TextField
                        margin="dense"
                        id="email"
                        label="email"
                        type="email"
                        fullWidth
                    />
                    <TextField
                        margin="dense"
                        id="telefone"
                        label="telefone"
                        type="text"
                        fullWidth
                    />
                    <TextField
                        margin="dense"
                        id="celular"
                        label="celular"
                        type="text"
                        fullWidth
                    />  
                    <TextField
                        margin="dense"
                        id="cep"
                        label="CEP"
                        type="text"
                    />
                    <TextField
                        margin="dense"
                        id="telefone"
                        label="telefone"
                        type="text"
                    />
                    <TextField
                        className = {styles.marginRight}
                        margin="dense"
                        id="uf"
                        label="cód. uf"
                        type="text"
                    />
                    <TextField
                        className = {styles.marginRight}
                        margin="dense"
                        id="cidade"
                        label="cidade"
                        type="text"
                    ></TextField>
                    <TextField
                        className = {styles.marginRight}
                        margin="dense"
                        id="municipio"
                        label="município"
                        type="text"
                    />
                    <TextField
                        className = {styles.marginRight}
                        margin="dense"
                        id="sexo"
                        label="sexo"
                        type="text"
                    />
                    <TextField
                        className = {styles.marginRight}
                        InputLabelProps={{ shrink: true }}
                        margin="dense"
                        id="data_nascimento"
                        label="data de nascimento"
                        type="date"
                    />       
    {/* "codigo_faixa_etaria": 1,
    "codigo_estado_civil": 1,
    "classe_social": "M",
    "codigo_instrucao": 1,
    "codigo_renda": 1,
    "codigo_profissao": 1,
    "codigo_posicao_trabalho": 1,
    "imovel": "praia",
    "funcionario": "empregada",
    "moradia": "Casa propria",
    "possui_carro": 1,
    "raca": "branca" */}
                </DialogContent>
                <DialogActions>
                <Button onClick={() => this.props.close(false)} color="primary">
                    Cancelar
                </Button>
                <Button onClick={this.handleClose} color="primary">
                    Adicionar
                </Button>
                </DialogActions>
          </Dialog>
        );
    }
}

export default withStyles(styles)(AddPessoa);
